Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:16.15,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H040000&\blur0.667\bord0\b1}Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,While Benio, completely drunk, got into a fight,{さすらいの弱って酒乱の花の乱れ咲き}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.20,0:01:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu was looking for her through all the town.{少尉はbenioを探せの大暴れとは次知らず}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Ushigorou hurried to the count to receive reinforcements,{一方ushigorouは援軍を迎えに伊集院伯爵家に走ったが}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,only to cause even more trouble!{この援軍がはた迷惑な醍醐味線}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.47,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Lieutenant?{大丈夫でありますか中佐殿}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This old man is out of his mind!{大変な爺さんにうちあがった}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,After Shinobu finally arrived, there was no time to cheer,{やっと少尉が現れてやれ嬉しいやもうほんの地下の間}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as his opponent happened to be his superior, who has now lost it!{喧嘩の相手はなんと少尉の上官でたっぷり恨みを買いました}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just the beginning of an endless tragedy!{これが底なしの悲劇のきっかけになろうと}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:03.91,Sign,,0,0,133,,{\fade(1000,300)\c&HF4F3FD&\bord0\b1\blur0.667}Episode 19\N{\fs86.667}Fleeting Happiness {つかの間の幸せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Uhm, you haven't paid for tonight yet.{あのあのまだお勘定頂いてないんですけども}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pay her.{払っとけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but...{あ、しかし}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and pay!{払えって言ったら払っとけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Proprietress, how much is it?{女将いくらだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 50.000 yen.{五十千円です}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.89,0:02:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There!{ほら}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged!{ありがとうございました}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ho-ho, haven't you forgot anything?{お前って退散か}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, don't forget your things!{はい、これ忘れ物よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you, those are a soldier's soul!{軍人の魂をよくも}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A soldier's soul? Gimme those, Ranko.{何が魂じゃ貸してみろ蘭子}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A stupid sword is supposed to be your soul?\NTake a look!{魂を日本刀じゃ見ており}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious saber!{わしの大事なサーべルを}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If a soldier's soul depends on that tin trash, the Japanese Army won't have a bright future.{そんなブリキのクズを魂というようじゃ日本の軍人も先が見えてくるな}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a grown-up, and yet you're so childish...{年寄りと思って仕立てに出ていれば}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking for more?{まだやるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You forgot something else.{あら、もう一つ忘れ物よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another piece of your soul.{大事な魂}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There it goes!{それ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurts, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you...{己}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mr. Lieutenant?{何、中佐さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Making fool of officials... I'll remember this.{軍人をバカにしようって覚えており}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.43,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Hey, we're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go home too.{さ、我々も帰ろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a triumphant return!{凱旋じゃあ凱旋じゃあ}\NHip hip, hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Count, you're awesome!{おじい様(?)い}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's return home as well.{では、我々も戻りましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.65,0:03:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, whoops, oh, eh?{ええ……お、おっと、あら、あら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.12,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to me?{わらしどうしたのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw-aw-aw-aw-aw, my head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?{どうした}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the fight's over, my head is spinning.{気が抜けたら良いが回ってきたみたいなのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I embarrassed myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm spinning round!{地球が回る}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2223D9&\3c&H75DCF0&\blur0.667\b1}Bam! {idk really what sound to make of it, some slam?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we go home like this?{こうして帰ればいいでしょ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!{だめです}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so embarassing!{こんなの恥ずかしいじゃないですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so embarrassing? It's just a husband carrying his wife on his back.{夫が妻を背負うのです何の恥ずかしいこと がありましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wife?!{\i0} Wife... He said wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wife?! Wife! Wife? Never! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.82,Sign,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Let go of me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got it, that's what a husband does,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.43,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but please look at what you've done for a moment!{ちょっとちょっと見てくださいよこの有様}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Five chairs, three desks, decanters, glasses and plates, for a total of... let's see...{椅子5個机三卓ちょうしとコップと皿が}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:22.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,Never! Never! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise, I'll pay for everything.{すいませんすべて弁償しますから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:26.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,Just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about paying her back!{こんなの弁償しなくてもいいの}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.12,0:05:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna give someone like you money!{あんたなんかに払ってもらいたくないわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll fall if you keep struggling like that!{そんなに暴れると危ないですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shut up, you! Shut it, you all!{うるさい　うるさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Benio?{大丈夫ですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And one pillar too.{それに柱一本}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD3D8D6&\3c&H316A75&}Puff {idk what to make of this sound effect as well, would surmise some sound of soul leaving the body or such}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A messenger came from the mountain village...{花咲かば　告げんといひし　山里の}{https://manyuraku.exblog.jp/24288183/}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He came from the mountain village riding a horse...{告げんといひし　山里の}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell everyone that the cherries had blossomed...{使いは来たり　馬に鞍}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The double cherry blossoms on the Kurama Mountain...{鞍馬の山の　うづ桜}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The count's rather joyful, what is he chanting though?{爺さんだいぶごきげんのようだけどなんだ いあの念仏はよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurama Tengu noh song.{謡曲鞍馬天狗}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you so gloomy, Ranmaru?{おい、何がおくれてんの欄ノ字}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like this exact same thing happened a long time ago...{ずーっと昔これとそっくり同じことがあっ たみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Being carried on someone's broad back...{ガッシリとした広い肩におんぶされて}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was... my father?{あれはお父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No...\NNo, it can't be.{いいえいいえ違うわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my father.{お父様ではない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it... Was it someone I don't know?{誰か誰か知らない人}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fated to be carried on that strong man's back...{私はそのたくましい人に負ぶさる運命だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It was decided from the very beginning.{ずっと昔からその運命は決まっていった}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,But who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?{誰なのその人}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I slept so well!{よく寝た}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So dazzling!{眩しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good m-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you already awake, Benio?{もうお目覚めでございますか紅緒様}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening?{つーことはなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world did I return to here?{私この家に帰ってきちゃったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to living with you again from now onward.{また今日からよろしくお願いいたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Hurts!{あ、痛ー}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? A bruise on my head?{なんだろう、頭が}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh darn! How could this happen all of a sudden?{やだこんな大きな事どうしたんだろういつの間に}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you remember?{覚えてないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shi-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning. Feeling better already?{おはよう御機嫌いかがですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened yesterday is so like you!{昨日のこと 全く紅緒さんらしいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, when did this bruise appear?{それにしてもこのゴブいつできたのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't recall?{本当に覚えがないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back home, I quarreled with my father{私の家に帰ってお父様と言い合いをして}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I drank a bit of alcohol with Ushigorou and Ranmaru.{牛ゴロウと蘭丸と3人でお酒をちょっぴり 飲んだまではなんとか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just "a bit of alcohol"?{お酒をちょっぴり}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember that much, but after that...{そこまで私もでもその後が}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember at all!{全然記憶が途絶える}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny? I'm worried, you know!{何ですか 笑うことないでしょ人が不安になってるっていうのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this is too like you!{すいませんあまりにあなたらしくて}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it here?{この辺でございますか}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! Be gentler!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you would have back pain again if you strained yourself at this age?{年甲斐もなく無茶をなさるからぎっくり腰が再発するのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?\NIf only you saw yesterday night's heroic feat!{何を申す？昨夜の大活躍見せたかったぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I knocked out every soldier, one after another
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and in the end they ran away out of fear!{さすがの兵隊殿もたちだつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's wrong with you? Are you deaf?{おい ほら人の言うこと聞いておらんのかお前}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, just come here and watch what's happening.{いいから午前もここおいでになってごらんそばせ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what you stopped massaging me for.{わしはマッサージをやめて良いとは言っておらんのだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's such a nice spectacle, isn't it, my Dear?{ほら、いい眺めではございませんか、ご前}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru and Chimaru are really healthy, heh!{てんまるとちまるが元気そうじゃな}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not about dogs!{犬のことではございません}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But...{しかし}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio has finally returned here.{Benioさんがやっと元の鞘に戻ったの ですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this is only thanks to yesterday night's heroic feat!{これも全て昨夜わしが8人突起の大活躍をしたなれば こそじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is bragging the only thing you can do?{そんな武勇自慢しかお口に出せないのですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are making thriving flowers bloom in this old mansion.{あの人たちはこの古い家に新しい花を咲かせてくれるのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If they have children at some point,{二人の間に子供が生まれるば}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,they will be our grandsons.{それは私たちのひ孫になるのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware!{わかっておる}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I may seem like a rustic person, but in reality{わしのような無骨者は物の哀れを感じても}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am just bad at expressing my emotions!{なんと表現して良いのやら苦手なのじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I also wish nothing but happiness to those two.{わしとってもあの二人の幸せを願う気持ちは誰にも引けを取りはせる}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if I was so messed up,{でもそんなに(?)していたんなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,how the hell did I come back here?{どうやって帰ってきたのかしら一体}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be on Ushigorou's rickshaw?{ushigorouの人力車だもん}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Might be. Who knows?{でしょうね多分}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.44,0:11:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.\NI'm dead sure someone carried me on his back.{違うわ私は 確か負ぶさって帰ってきたんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But on whose back?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now!{思い出した}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Who carried you on his back?{誰に背負われたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was just a dream,{あれはきっと夢の中の出来事で}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in reality I got home on my own.{本当は誰にも負ぶされなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My impossible love{私の叶わぬ恋が}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.41,0:11:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,can finally flourish after all this time{孫のしのぶさんの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,thanks to my grandson Shinobu.{やっと実るのですね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be a happy couple.{幸せになるんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please overcome any difficulty you might face in life.{どんなことがあろうともそれを乗り越えてね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that got me really worked up!{それでね私とっても焦っちゃったのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. This is the perfect day to tell her my feelings.{そうだ今日こそ僕の心を紅緒さんに行って しまおう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I think it suits you.{はい、綺麗でしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?{改まって何}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's...{ずっと}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.32,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,something I've always wanted to tell you.{あなたに話そうと考えていたことがあるのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I...{僕は}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinobu!\NLook, look!{ほら少尉こら見て見て}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so unusual!{めずらしいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Those cockroaches are flying in group!{ゴキブリが集団で飛んでる}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They're in single file now!{さおになった}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A hook shape now!{こんどはかぎよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't you think it's unusual?{ねえ、めずらしいでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, what did you want to tell me?{ところで何の話でしたっけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, what's wrong?{あらやだどうかなさったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling ill?{気分でも悪いの}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, listen to me.{ねぇ少尉ったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.\NI'll talk about it another day.{いやいいですよいずれその話はまた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...{でも}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the right mood for this topic.{こういう話はムードが大切ですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be leaving soon.{僕そろそろ出かけなければ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later, Benio.{じゃあまたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So strange...{変な、少尉}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He could've just said it.\NThat guy's truly weird.{はっきり言えばいいのに、ほんとテンポずれてんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in a place like this?{何してんのよこんなところで}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.94,0:13:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell by looking? I'm working out.{視ればわかるでしょう体を鍛えてるの }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.98,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But won't this damage your delicate fingers?{だってそんなことしたらあんたの大事な白魚の指が}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Benio.{安心してよbenio-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't trust that Sublieutenant,{少尉なんか頼りにしないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one protecting you!{僕がbenioさんを守るからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it,{どうもよくわからん}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,something must've happened last night.{やっぱり昨夜何かあったのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lady Benio!{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, morning!{おはようよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.99,0:14:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's this voice?{なんだ、何かしらの声}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds like Ranko.{蘭子さんみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot!{やばい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What could she be doing?{何してるのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see!{行ってみましょうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!\NE-Erm, don't go!{待って、ダメ行っちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?{どうしてですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you go there... Well, you...{それはあのーその}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Ranko is one of us, isn't she?{だって蘭子さんは大切な仲間なんですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds about right. {\i1}Right?{\i0}{そうですかわ、ねえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beg your pardon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not looking good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, girls?{どうかなさったの皆さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you making strange sounds all along?{蘭子さんこそここで変な声出していなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was exercising.{あれ 体操してたのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Exercising?{ 体操}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, calisthenics.{そう 美容体操}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it was calisthenics.{あら美容体操やってらしたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!\NI also want to become as pretty as Ranko!{素敵私も蘭子さんみたいに美しくなりたいわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us lessons from now on!{明日から私に教えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!{お願いします}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We're begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?\NOkay, then.{そうねいいわよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go now?{じゃ行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! They didn't unmask him!{良かったばれないですんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be going, Benio.{では行ってくるよBenioさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home safe!{いってらっしゃい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home safe, Young Master.{いってらっしゃいませ若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Boss, we gotta go in a couple minutes, y'know.{あの親分そろそろお出かけのお時間です}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.46,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Where to?{どこへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too carefree!{全くのんきなお人ですな}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to skip school?{学校サボるんでやんすかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hurry up to board.{さ、早く乗って}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H191A1F&\3c&HDADDDF&\b1\blur0.667}Boss Benio's car {I don't really remember how I tled this last time}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a student, Boss.{親分はまだ女学生なんですぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...{そうだっけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So much happened that I had completely forgotten about school!{あんまりいろんなことがあるもんで小学校のことなんかすっかり忘れてたわっ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So this means that you haven't done any homework...{てことは\N宿題なんかもまるきり}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally!{もちろん}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's just call it a day off for today.{それじゃとりあえず今日のところはずる休みとして扱い}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All settled!{決定}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.46,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first smart thing you've ever said since I met you!{あんた私と知り合って初めていいことを言ったわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm learning from my Boss!{この親分にしてこの 子分なり}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll just go to town for some business.{出しゃれ街へ出てちょいとしとか席}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let me know if you need anything, Boss!{それじゃ、(?)からね親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin... Is it here?{伊集院ここか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful building.\NGood for me, they'll pay me in no time!{立派な門だねこのお屋敷ならないね}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do- what do you want from me?!{あたしゃ、あたしのものじゃないんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Rickshawman, help me!{車屋さん助けて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you last night's proprietress?{夕べの飲み屋の女将じゃねえか}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I am, I'm here to give this bill to the sublieutenant.{そうなんだよ、あたしゃね少尉さんに請求書を届けに来たんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go?{じゃ行くがいやな}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.49,0:17:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop, hop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.33,0:17:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do something about these dogs.{この犬なんとかしておくれよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you!{ごしょうだからさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that, these dogs are my nemesis.{ダメダメおいらだって毎度悩まされてんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:18:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Proprietress, I don't wanna be rude, but you better turn around and take another path.{おかみさん悪いことやねん命が惜しかっ たらこのまま手ぶらで蹴った方が身のため だぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.79,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a threat?{脅かしくなったよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you only got one life, so be careful!{ま一つしかね命だ大事にしなよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not joking! My life depends on this, you know!{冗談じゃないよこっちは生活がかかってるんです からね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then I'll just go the other way.{いいよいいよここがダメならあっちがあるんだhttps://youtu.be/GA3uDD66byI}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot come near here.{ここへ近寄ってはいかん}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to ask you a favour...{それがお願いがありまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened?{おいどうしたんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she want?{そこの民間人}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm, actually, I'd like to give this to Sublieutenant Ijuuin.{ああ、あの、実はここの伊集院少尉様にこれを}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open, come in.{よし、入れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a request for you, Sublieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman has just visited to give you this...{ただいま民間人が少尉殿の訪ねてまいりましてこのようなものを}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she really went all the way here.{なんだこんなところまで来たのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it, so please tell her{よしわかった 間違いなく払うからと}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'll pay for everything.{使いのものにそう言ってくれたまえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir, understood!{帰ります}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.{これってよしと}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I am, what do you need?{入ります}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a favour.{ちょっと使いに行ってくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you please forward the documents on the desk to Lieutenant Innen?{その机の上の書類を師団本部の印念中佐に届けてくれないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.18,0:19:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir, understood!{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.84,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do it right away.{これを印念中佐殿にお届けするのであり ます}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving.{失礼します}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks.{あ、頼んだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.64,Sign,,0,0,0,,Main Administrative Office {本部事務室 - not sure what to make of it, seems to be very serious house of officialdom where they handle a lot of papers}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so furious.{全く忌忌しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That hoyden is Hanamura's daughter...{花村の娘とは言っとったのやつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.71,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about her irritates me!{思い出しても腹の立つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it? Do you need anything, Lieutenant?{何か私にご用でありますか}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.{いやべつに}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{そうなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Commander Hanamura.{やぁ花札さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Innen,{大事だいたい第三中隊}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.07,0:20:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sublieutenant Ijuuin sent me here.{伊集院shouiの登板編参りました - just took it from the italian version}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? From Sublieutenant Ijuuin?{何 伊集院少尉}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir, he told me to give you this.{はこれをお届けするようにと}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, thank you.{よし ご苦労}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin, huh...{伊集院め}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He ignores our military rule of no long hair{長髪禁止の我が軍の規則を無視してからに}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's not even a pure Japanese.{おまけに純生の日本人でもないくせに}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand him being in the Sacred Imperial Army!{神聖なる帝国陸軍にいるのも我慢ならん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no choice but to give him tit for tat.{なんとかして仕返ししてやらねば気が済まぬ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A refund for five chairs, three desks, decanters, glasses and plates?{椅子五個、机三、ちょうしとコップと皿の弁償金}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?{なんじゃこりゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.95,0:21:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it about yesterday night?{夕べの飲み屋の弁償金か}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ijuuin again...{もう伊集院め}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He sent me this bill to make me pay for it, didn't he?{これわしに払わせようと付けを回してよこしたんだな}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's gone too far!{もう許せん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just unacceptable!{断じているせん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out of his mind!{変わった変わった}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Innen's red flag was clear as day.{印念中佐の危険信号は青だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.11,0:21:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a war front in Russia.{おーロシア戦線に}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.92,0:21:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We might need to dispatch our soldiers alongside Americans in Siberia.{我が軍もアメリカと共にシベリアへ出兵することになるかもしれん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll show them our power.{腕が鳴るな}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It is 1918 and Japan is on the verge of dispatching troops to Siberia.{時は大正7年、日本はシベリア出兵を目前に控えていた}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatching troops to Russia...{ロシア出兵か}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This could work...{こいつは利用できそうだぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Pretty, aren't they?{ほら、綺麗でしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The gentle breeze of love has turned into a violent typhoon all of a sudden.{ロマンチックなそよ風がいつのまにやら台風となって}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it completely blow away our High Collar Lady's happiness?{はいからさんの幸せを根こそぎ吹き飛ばしてしまうのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is happiness just a fleeting dream?{幸せは 束の間の儚い夢なのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger!{危うし}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger, High Collar Lady!{危うしはいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady now trusts Shinobu, not caring about his mountain of love letters,{少尉を信じるハイカラさんは\N山のラブレター気にもせず}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and she decides to go shopping in Gofukubashi.{呉服橋までショッピング}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, unfortunately, she stumbles across Shinobu's date, and his partner{だがこともあろうに少尉のデートの現場を目撃する羽目になろうとは}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is none other than the beautiful geisha Hananoya Kichiji.{相手は美人芸者のはなのやきちじ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So what are you gonna do?{さてどうする}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, High Collar Lady?{どうするするハイカラさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time in Here Comes Miss Modern:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Two lovers, don't miss it!{相合傘のお二人はお楽しみに}
